OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny remaining overnight rain
OL,6,Fwill soon clear east then sunny spells
OL,7,Fand showers. Drier for a time in the
OL,8,Fafternoon before further showers
OL,9,Flater, heavy at times. Cool and
OL,10,Fblustery.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FScattered to frequent
OL,13,Fblustery showers feed in from the west
OL,14,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,15,Fthese showers heavy at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool with
OL,18,Fsunny spells and scattered heavy
OL,19,Fshowers. Blustery winds around the
OL,20,Fcoast. Chance of overnight frost in
OL,21,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
